scenes.description: Raora Panthera takes her turn in the Speed Block game, successfully completing several levels including stacking, posing, and a math problem while her teammates cheer and give advice.
Cecilia Immergreen takes her turn, doing well initially but failing the final level under pressure, leading to an explosion that transforms her into a shadow entity.
The group reacts to Cecilia's transformation. Cecilia, now a shadow, jokes about her score and fingers. Elizabeth prepares for the next round.
